1
00:00:06,929 --> 00:00:08,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think it's too late to ask for forgiveness?</font>

2
00:00:08,459 --> 00:00:09,489
<font color=#FFFF00>(Episode 39)</font>

3
00:00:09,821 --> 00:00:12,691
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you think your wrongdoing would be justified if you raise Sang Woo?</font>

4
00:00:13,489 --> 00:00:16,989
<font color=#FFFF00>I know I don't deserve to be forgiven.</font>

5
00:00:18,089 --> 00:00:19,129
<font color=#FFFF00>I've ruined...</font>

6
00:00:19,729 --> 00:00:21,389
<font color=#FFFF00>a guy's life.</font>

7
00:00:23,089 --> 00:00:25,159
<font color=#FFFF00>And his young children have gone...</font>

8
00:00:25,529 --> 00:00:27,159
<font color=#FFFF00>through a lot because of me.</font>

9
00:00:28,459 --> 00:00:30,159
<font color=#FFFF00>How could I be forgiven?</font>

10
00:00:31,489 --> 00:00:33,299
<font color=#FFFF00>If you know that well,</font>

11
00:00:33,959 --> 00:00:35,529
<font color=#FFFF00>why did you come here?</font>

12
00:00:36,759 --> 00:00:37,929
<font color=#FFFF00>I need you to leave now.</font>

13
00:00:38,389 --> 00:00:40,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Leave already!</font>

14
00:00:40,959 --> 00:00:41,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Before that,</font>

15
00:00:43,189 --> 00:00:44,789
<font color=#FFFF00>please let me ask you a favor.</font>

16
00:00:47,189 --> 00:00:48,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Please...</font>

17
00:00:49,229 --> 00:00:50,589
<font color=#FFFF00>leave...</font>

18
00:00:51,929 --> 00:00:54,689
<font color=#FFFF00>with Seong Joon as soon as possible.</font>

19
00:00:56,189 --> 00:00:57,359
<font color=#FFFF00>My family thinks...</font>

20
00:00:58,859 --> 00:01:01,729
<font color=#FFFF00>he's my own son.</font>

21
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:06,159
<font color=#FFFF00>But...</font>

22
00:01:07,389 --> 00:01:10,129
<font color=#FFFF00>if they find out that he's not my son...</font>

23
00:01:11,659 --> 00:01:14,459
<font color=#FFFF00>but the driver's son,</font>

24
00:01:16,729 --> 00:01:18,559
<font color=#FFFF00>they will abandon...</font>

25
00:01:18,689 --> 00:01:20,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon coldly.</font>

26
00:01:22,729 --> 00:01:24,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Then they will blame...</font>

27
00:01:24,859 --> 00:01:26,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon...</font>

28
00:01:26,789 --> 00:01:28,429
<font color=#FFFF00>for everything.</font>

29
00:01:32,659 --> 00:01:34,759
<font color=#FFFF00>So what does it have to do with us?</font>

30
00:01:35,889 --> 00:01:37,159
<font color=#FFFF00>We no longer...</font>

31
00:01:38,089 --> 00:01:40,259
<font color=#FFFF00>want to be entangled with you.</font>

32
00:01:40,889 --> 00:01:42,629
<font color=#FFFF00>That'd be better for me as well.</font>

33
00:01:42,989 --> 00:01:44,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Before it's too late,</font>

34
00:01:46,489 --> 00:01:48,159
<font color=#FFFF00>before everyone finds out the truth,</font>

35
00:01:50,659 --> 00:01:53,429
<font color=#FFFF00>please leave with Seong Joon.</font>

36
00:01:54,859 --> 00:01:56,729
<font color=#FFFF00>That's for Seong Joon's sake.</font>

37
00:01:57,659 --> 00:01:58,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Why?</font>

38
00:01:59,789 --> 00:02:02,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you afraid that your family will know what you've done in the past?</font>

39
00:02:02,989 --> 00:02:06,189
<font color=#FFFF00>You used to be a good father, a good husband, and a good neighbor.</font>

40
00:02:06,659 --> 00:02:09,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Now you're afraid that others might find out your true colors?</font>

41
00:02:09,859 --> 00:02:11,899
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that why you took Sang Woo away from me and raised him?</font>

42
00:02:12,929 --> 00:02:14,789
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you try to cover your sins like this?</font>

43
00:02:17,559 --> 00:02:18,859
<font color=#FFFF00>You're such a coward and a scum.</font>

44
00:02:19,429 --> 00:02:20,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo!</font>

45
00:02:27,829 --> 00:02:29,859
<font color=#FFFF00>- Please stop. - See?</font>

46
00:02:30,859 --> 00:02:33,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Now you know who this guy you believed to be your dad...</font>

47
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,029
<font color=#FFFF00>really is!</font>

48
00:02:45,459 --> 00:02:46,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Please get up.</font>

49
00:02:57,059 --> 00:02:58,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go home.</font>

50
00:03:00,529 --> 00:03:01,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

51
00:03:02,429 --> 00:03:03,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

52
00:03:05,889 --> 00:03:06,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Sang Woo.</font>

53
00:03:11,629 --> 00:03:12,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Sang Woo!</font>

54
00:03:15,629 --> 00:03:17,029
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

55
00:03:18,859 --> 00:03:20,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me walk him home.</font>

56
00:03:21,659 --> 00:03:22,729
<font color=#FFFF00>We can talk later.</font>

57
00:03:25,689 --> 00:03:27,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go, Dad.</font>

58
00:03:30,589 --> 00:03:32,559
<font color=#FFFF00>- Seong Joon... - Hurry up.</font>

59
00:04:24,989 --> 00:04:26,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

60
00:04:30,229 --> 00:04:32,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Go to your brother.</font>

61
00:04:33,429 --> 00:04:34,699
<font color=#FFFF00>Go to your brother.</font>

62
00:04:36,629 --> 00:04:37,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me take you home.</font>

63
00:04:39,289 --> 00:04:40,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey.</font>

64
00:04:43,259 --> 00:04:45,989
<font color=#FFFF00>You should be cursing me out and kicking me with him.</font>

65
00:04:46,889 --> 00:04:48,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this?</font>

66
00:04:49,329 --> 00:04:50,859
<font color=#FFFF00>You shouldn't be nice to me.</font>

67
00:04:52,389 --> 00:04:53,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Go to him now.</font>

68
00:04:56,789 --> 00:04:58,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't say anything.</font>

69
00:05:00,529 --> 00:05:01,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go.</font>

70
00:05:09,059 --> 00:05:10,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

71
00:05:10,629 --> 00:05:12,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Sik. Spread the blankets for him.</font>

72
00:05:12,229 --> 00:05:14,429
<font color=#FFFF00>What? Okay. I'm going.</font>

73
00:05:14,429 --> 00:05:16,729
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hey. Hyung Seop. - Honey. What's wrong?</font>

74
00:05:16,729 --> 00:05:18,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon. What's wrong with him?</font>

75
00:05:18,129 --> 00:05:20,429
<font color=#FFFF00>He was fine a little while ago. What's going on?</font>

76
00:05:20,429 --> 00:05:21,589
<font color=#FFFF00>- Goodness. - Oh my.</font>

77
00:05:21,929 --> 00:05:24,629
<font color=#FFFF00>- Slowly. Be careful. - Hyung Seop.</font>

78
00:05:24,729 --> 00:05:27,489
<font color=#FFFF00>- What's up with him? - Dad. Should we go to the hospital?</font>

79
00:05:27,589 --> 00:05:29,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad. Should I take you there?</font>

80
00:05:29,689 --> 00:05:31,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyung Seop. Pull yourself together.</font>

81
00:05:31,789 --> 00:05:34,229
<font color=#FFFF00>What's gotten into you lately?</font>

82
00:05:34,229 --> 00:05:36,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Seong Joon. Where did you go with Dad?</font>

83
00:05:38,629 --> 00:05:40,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey. Why can't you answer me?</font>

84
00:05:40,329 --> 00:05:43,029
<font color=#FFFF00>He was fine when he went out, but now he's not in good condition.</font>

85
00:05:43,259 --> 00:05:44,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Where did you go?</font>

86
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,289
<font color=#FFFF00>I will tell you later.</font>

87
00:05:47,729 --> 00:05:48,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you hear him?</font>

88
00:05:49,529 --> 00:05:51,429
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you act so rude?</font>

89
00:05:52,029 --> 00:05:54,089
<font color=#FFFF00>You ought to answer when I ask you a question.</font>

90
00:05:54,229 --> 00:05:55,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are you going now?</font>

91
00:05:56,729 --> 00:05:58,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Leave him alone.</font>

92
00:06:00,229 --> 00:06:02,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't bother him.</font>

93
00:06:02,259 --> 00:06:03,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

94
00:06:24,329 --> 00:06:25,759
<font color=#FFFF00>What is he doing again?</font>

95
00:06:32,989 --> 00:06:34,259
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing now?</font>

96
00:06:34,559 --> 00:06:36,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you really have to do this?</font>

97
00:06:36,789 --> 00:06:37,789
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

98
00:06:37,889 --> 00:06:38,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway,</font>

99
00:06:39,489 --> 00:06:41,989
<font color=#FFFF00>he is just a poor, weak old man.</font>

100
00:06:44,589 --> 00:06:46,659
<font color=#FFFF00>What is your point?</font>

101
00:06:46,859 --> 00:06:47,889
<font color=#FFFF00>You are right.</font>

102
00:06:48,189 --> 00:06:49,689
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a bad person.</font>

103
00:06:50,289 --> 00:06:52,189
<font color=#FFFF00>He shouldn't have done that,</font>

104
00:06:52,189 --> 00:06:53,529
<font color=#FFFF00>no matter how precious his children were to him.</font>

105
00:06:53,689 --> 00:06:55,029
<font color=#FFFF00>He shouldn't have mistreated and ignored...</font>

106
00:06:55,129 --> 00:06:58,629
<font color=#FFFF00>poor people just because he had money.</font>

107
00:06:58,889 --> 00:07:01,629
<font color=#FFFF00>I also hate and despise that kind of people.</font>

108
00:07:01,729 --> 00:07:02,889
<font color=#FFFF00>If you know this,</font>

109
00:07:03,689 --> 00:07:05,529
<font color=#FFFF00>how can you take him outside in front of me?</font>

110
00:07:05,529 --> 00:07:08,729
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope you will calm down. If you don't,</font>

111
00:07:09,729 --> 00:07:12,089
<font color=#FFFF00>you are no better than my father 20 years ago.</font>

112
00:07:16,689 --> 00:07:18,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Who is your father?</font>

113
00:07:18,829 --> 00:07:21,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you still call him your father?</font>

114
00:07:22,329 --> 00:07:23,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Your father...</font>

115
00:07:23,829 --> 00:07:26,859
<font color=#FFFF00>wasn't a selfish old man. He was a poor bus driver.</font>

116
00:07:27,989 --> 00:07:30,459
<font color=#FFFF00>He had no connections or anyone to rely on.</font>

117
00:07:30,889 --> 00:07:32,329
<font color=#FFFF00>There wasn't a single person who'd listen to his complaints.</font>

118
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:35,589
<font color=#FFFF00>A pitiful bus driver who was penniless...</font>

119
00:07:35,929 --> 00:07:37,889
<font color=#FFFF00>- is your father. - I know.</font>

120
00:07:38,089 --> 00:07:40,259
<font color=#FFFF00>I know how my defenseless father passed away...</font>

121
00:07:40,259 --> 00:07:43,559
<font color=#FFFF00>and what mistake my current father made to him,</font>

122
00:07:44,059 --> 00:07:45,659
<font color=#FFFF00>- but... - No.</font>

123
00:07:46,529 --> 00:07:47,659
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't know.</font>

124
00:07:48,529 --> 00:07:49,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

125
00:08:20,229 --> 00:08:21,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know what this is?</font>

126
00:08:24,159 --> 00:08:26,589
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the tie our father hanged himself with.</font>

127
00:08:27,659 --> 00:08:30,159
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the tie Han Hyung Seop loosened...</font>

128
00:08:30,629 --> 00:08:32,189
<font color=#FFFF00>in order to beat up our father.</font>

129
00:08:33,429 --> 00:08:34,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Our father...</font>

130
00:08:35,989 --> 00:08:37,689
<font color=#FFFF00>picked this up and hanged himself.</font>

131
00:08:40,189 --> 00:08:41,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

132
00:08:44,859 --> 00:08:45,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you still feel...</font>

133
00:08:47,829 --> 00:08:50,229
<font color=#FFFF00>sympathy for that vicious man after seeing this?</font>

134
00:08:50,959 --> 00:08:52,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you still pity him?</font>

135
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:54,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Please...</font>

136
00:08:55,889 --> 00:08:57,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Please give me some time.</font>

137
00:08:57,859 --> 00:08:59,659
<font color=#FFFF00>How much more time do you need?</font>

138
00:08:59,929 --> 00:09:01,589
<font color=#FFFF00>I've been waiting for 23 years.</font>

139
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:03,859
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you everything.</font>

140
00:09:04,359 --> 00:09:06,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Even at this moment, I'm waiting for you.</font>

141
00:09:06,359 --> 00:09:08,489
<font color=#FFFF00>I need time to hate him.</font>

142
00:09:11,829 --> 00:09:13,529
<font color=#FFFF00>You had 23 years.</font>

143
00:09:15,229 --> 00:09:16,799
<font color=#FFFF00>I had only a few weeks.</font>

144
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:20,529
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sang Woo. - During the last 23 years,</font>

145
00:09:21,359 --> 00:09:23,229
<font color=#FFFF00>I trusted and followed my father.</font>

146
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:26,929
<font color=#FFFF00>During that time, my father wasn't a dead bus driver.</font>

147
00:09:27,889 --> 00:09:29,589
<font color=#FFFF00>It was Han Hyung Seop.</font>

148
00:09:33,689 --> 00:09:35,229
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a long period of time.</font>

149
00:09:36,189 --> 00:09:37,389
<font color=#FFFF00>How could I...</font>

150
00:09:38,129 --> 00:09:39,529
<font color=#FFFF00>throw away those years overnight?</font>

151
00:09:39,529 --> 00:09:41,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't be weak.</font>

152
00:09:41,529 --> 00:09:42,759
<font color=#FFFF00>You are not a kid.</font>

153
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:45,799
<font color=#FFFF00>So please. I beg of you to give me some time.</font>

154
00:09:47,459 --> 00:09:48,559
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you...</font>

155
00:09:49,589 --> 00:09:50,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

156
00:09:51,459 --> 00:09:52,459
<font color=#FFFF00>You...</font>

157
00:09:53,489 --> 00:09:55,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Get a grip!</font>

158
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:13,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom. I'm going out.</font>

159
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:16,589
<font color=#FFFF00>How's Dad?</font>

160
00:10:17,299 --> 00:10:18,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Can't you see?</font>

161
00:10:18,859 --> 00:10:21,089
<font color=#FFFF00>He hasn't moved an inch since last night.</font>

162
00:10:21,299 --> 00:10:23,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't bother Dad.</font>

163
00:10:23,429 --> 00:10:25,059
<font color=#FFFF00>You should ask Seong Joon.</font>

164
00:10:26,359 --> 00:10:27,759
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

165
00:10:27,859 --> 00:10:31,429
<font color=#FFFF00>I think the reason why he's acting like this has to do with Seong Joon.</font>

166
00:10:31,429 --> 00:10:33,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Bring Seong Joon and ask him.</font>

167
00:10:38,489 --> 00:10:39,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa.</font>

168
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:42,799
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop talking nonsense and just go.</font>

169
00:10:43,129 --> 00:10:46,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you all right? Can you sit up?</font>

170
00:10:46,629 --> 00:10:47,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

171
00:10:48,429 --> 00:10:50,429
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you to go.</font>

172
00:10:55,189 --> 00:10:56,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, I'm going.</font>

173
00:10:57,089 --> 00:10:58,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's talk tonight.</font>

174
00:11:10,859 --> 00:11:12,389
<font color=#FFFF00>- Are you going somewhere? - Yes.</font>

175
00:11:13,629 --> 00:11:16,189
<font color=#FFFF00>You should say your greetings in the morning properly and go.</font>

176
00:11:16,429 --> 00:11:18,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. She's so rude.</font>

177
00:11:22,359 --> 00:11:24,359
<font color=#FFFF00>So please tell me.</font>

178
00:11:24,359 --> 00:11:27,229
<font color=#FFFF00>What is going on with you these days?</font>

179
00:11:27,389 --> 00:11:28,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you feeling better?</font>

180
00:11:29,289 --> 00:11:32,029
<font color=#FFFF00>What was Jeong Hwa talking about?</font>

181
00:11:32,029 --> 00:11:34,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother mentioned something about that too.</font>

182
00:11:36,159 --> 00:11:39,389
<font color=#FFFF00>You told Mother that Seong Joon was not your son.</font>

183
00:11:39,689 --> 00:11:42,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you tell her that? What do you mean by that?</font>

184
00:11:43,259 --> 00:11:45,129
<font color=#FFFF00>- Honey. - Hyung Seop.</font>

185
00:11:46,129 --> 00:11:48,529
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what's going on with you.</font>

186
00:11:48,959 --> 00:11:51,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think it's better to...</font>

187
00:11:51,489 --> 00:11:54,829
<font color=#FFFF00>tell your mother and wife at least?</font>

188
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:58,229
<font color=#FFFF00>What you told me troubled me greatly.</font>

189
00:11:58,229 --> 00:11:59,729
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I told Jeong Ae what you told me.</font>

190
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:02,929
<font color=#FFFF00>I couldn't bear this by myself.</font>

191
00:12:03,089 --> 00:12:04,859
<font color=#FFFF00>So tell us. What happened?</font>

192
00:12:05,259 --> 00:12:07,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you bringing up Seong Joon's past now?</font>

193
00:12:08,489 --> 00:12:11,959
<font color=#FFFF00>You brought him home because you said he was your son.</font>

194
00:12:11,959 --> 00:12:14,289
<font color=#FFFF00>You said he was born out of wedlock.</font>

195
00:12:14,329 --> 00:12:16,429
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you tell us he's not your son now?</font>

196
00:12:16,589 --> 00:12:20,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't press him for an answer. Speak softly.</font>

197
00:12:20,359 --> 00:12:21,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother.</font>

198
00:12:21,889 --> 00:12:25,089
<font color=#FFFF00>I lived with this man for 40 years and he seems to be sly.</font>

199
00:12:25,089 --> 00:12:27,589
<font color=#FFFF00>20 years ago, he said he had an affair...</font>

200
00:12:27,589 --> 00:12:29,359
<font color=#FFFF00>and brought a child home.</font>

201
00:12:29,359 --> 00:12:31,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Now he's telling us that it wasn't true.</font>

202
00:12:31,289 --> 00:12:33,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Then whose family does he belong to?</font>

203
00:12:33,229 --> 00:12:36,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you turn someone else's son into yours and bring him home?</font>

204
00:12:37,329 --> 00:12:40,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Whom have I been raising for 20 years?</font>

205
00:12:40,829 --> 00:12:44,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, if this is the case, this is more aggravating.</font>

206
00:12:44,359 --> 00:12:47,489
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't have to feel aggravated by this.</font>

207
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:49,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's hear him out.</font>

208
00:12:50,089 --> 00:12:52,659
<font color=#FFFF00>He's not explaining himself.</font>

209
00:12:52,659 --> 00:12:55,329
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I feel more insulted and uncomfortable.</font>

210
00:12:56,189 --> 00:12:58,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey. Stop it. Ask Seong Joon when he comes back.</font>

211
00:12:58,459 --> 00:12:59,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Ask him if he knows something.</font>

212
00:13:01,189 --> 00:13:02,359
<font color=#FFFF00>By any chance,</font>

213
00:13:02,929 --> 00:13:04,659
<font color=#FFFF00>does Seong Joon know about this?</font>

214
00:13:05,059 --> 00:13:08,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that why you weren't getting alone well lately?</font>

215
00:13:10,089 --> 00:13:11,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that it?</font>

216
00:13:12,089 --> 00:13:13,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey.</font>

217
00:13:14,689 --> 00:13:17,289
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not the time for you to feel glum.</font>

218
00:13:19,529 --> 00:13:22,389
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not Ji Hoon's first time rebelling against you.</font>

219
00:13:22,889 --> 00:13:24,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Besides, does it really matter in what place he is ranked?</font>

220
00:13:24,729 --> 00:13:26,289
<font color=#FFFF00>What good is it if he's ranked first?</font>

221
00:13:27,229 --> 00:13:29,289
<font color=#FFFF00>The house he's living in now has been put up as a collateral.</font>

222
00:13:29,329 --> 00:13:32,259
<font color=#FFFF00>His father will be a manager of a fried chicken restaurant...</font>

223
00:13:32,259 --> 00:13:34,389
<font color=#FFFF00>or a mediocre lawyer if things keep going as it is now.</font>

224
00:13:34,429 --> 00:13:38,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Someone needs to come up with a plan to lead this family.</font>

225
00:13:40,259 --> 00:13:41,259
<font color=#FFFF00>So what?</font>

226
00:13:41,659 --> 00:13:43,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Who's going to lead this family?</font>

227
00:13:44,129 --> 00:13:45,729
<font color=#FFFF00>It will be me, of course.</font>

228
00:13:45,729 --> 00:13:47,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Please know your place.</font>

229
00:13:47,529 --> 00:13:49,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Because of you,</font>

230
00:13:49,659 --> 00:13:51,229
<font color=#FFFF00>the children are bullied at school.</font>

231
00:13:51,289 --> 00:13:52,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell them to wait a bit.</font>

232
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:57,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell them their father will return as a new, reformed man.</font>

233
00:13:57,089 --> 00:14:00,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't just think about your success.</font>

234
00:14:00,489 --> 00:14:03,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Try to get Ji Hoon to study again.</font>

235
00:14:03,189 --> 00:14:06,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo is excelling at singing,</font>

236
00:14:06,329 --> 00:14:08,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon's grades has dramatically gone down.</font>

237
00:14:08,759 --> 00:14:12,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo isn't the type to nag Ji Hoon to study.</font>

238
00:14:13,689 --> 00:14:15,429
<font color=#FFFF00>It might help if I don't see him.</font>

239
00:14:15,589 --> 00:14:16,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Living in the same house isn't helping.</font>

240
00:14:16,859 --> 00:14:18,889
<font color=#FFFF00>- I'm about to lose my mind. - Shut it!</font>

241
00:14:19,129 --> 00:14:20,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Be quiet!</font>

242
00:14:20,989 --> 00:14:22,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

243
00:14:22,189 --> 00:14:25,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Can't you really think about someone else than your children?</font>

244
00:14:26,059 --> 00:14:28,929
<font color=#FFFF00>The grown-ups must be successful for the children to be successful.</font>

245
00:14:28,929 --> 00:14:30,759
<font color=#FFFF00>He's only in his third year of middle school.</font>

246
00:14:30,759 --> 00:14:34,359
<font color=#FFFF00>It will take forever for a teenager to restore his family.</font>

247
00:14:34,429 --> 00:14:36,859
<font color=#FFFF00>- So what's your plan? - Why do you even ask?</font>

248
00:14:37,089 --> 00:14:40,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Now that he wants to make money by getting a mortgage,</font>

249
00:14:41,089 --> 00:14:43,059
<font color=#FFFF00>I will regain...</font>

250
00:14:43,159 --> 00:14:45,729
<font color=#FFFF00>the tarnished reputation of our family using my old fame.</font>

251
00:14:45,889 --> 00:14:47,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Reputation is money, right?</font>

252
00:14:47,989 --> 00:14:50,459
<font color=#FFFF00>I will make some money with the reputation...</font>

253
00:14:50,689 --> 00:14:53,329
<font color=#FFFF00>and get out of this house as soon as possible...</font>

254
00:14:53,359 --> 00:14:55,729
<font color=#FFFF00>and no longer argue with my brother. Okay?</font>

255
00:14:55,889 --> 00:14:57,529
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll move out of this house.</font>

256
00:14:59,859 --> 00:15:01,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey, where are you going?</font>

257
00:15:01,759 --> 00:15:04,259
<font color=#FFFF00>You should go talk to Ji Hoon. Honey!</font>

258
00:15:05,489 --> 00:15:06,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

259
00:15:09,189 --> 00:15:11,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are you going?</font>

260
00:15:11,589 --> 00:15:13,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Hang on a second.</font>

261
00:15:15,359 --> 00:15:16,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

262
00:15:17,159 --> 00:15:18,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh my goodness.</font>

263
00:15:19,389 --> 00:15:21,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Where on earth are we going?</font>

264
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:23,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Aren't you going to tell me?</font>

265
00:15:31,729 --> 00:15:32,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Get off the car.</font>

266
00:15:54,489 --> 00:15:55,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are we?</font>

267
00:15:57,959 --> 00:16:00,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you going to bury me because I'm against your business?</font>

268
00:16:02,559 --> 00:16:03,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Why would I bury you?</font>

269
00:16:04,459 --> 00:16:07,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Why would I bury my wife who spent half her life with me?</font>

270
00:16:08,759 --> 00:16:12,529
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm here to show you how you will live in comfort...</font>

271
00:16:12,889 --> 00:16:14,159
<font color=#FFFF00>from now on.</font>

272
00:16:15,859 --> 00:16:18,189
<font color=#FFFF00>- Live in comfort? - Hye Joo.</font>

273
00:16:18,989 --> 00:16:20,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Watch carefully.</font>

274
00:16:22,629 --> 00:16:25,159
<font color=#FFFF00>From here to there,</font>

275
00:16:25,229 --> 00:16:27,929
<font color=#FFFF00>there will be the main building of the theme park.</font>

276
00:16:28,129 --> 00:16:31,359
<font color=#FFFF00>There will be amenities for visitors over there.</font>

277
00:16:31,889 --> 00:16:33,859
<font color=#FFFF00>And over there will be...</font>

278
00:16:34,029 --> 00:16:36,589
<font color=#FFFF00>a huge aquarium.</font>

279
00:16:38,189 --> 00:16:40,759
<font color=#FFFF00>- Where? - Right over there.</font>

280
00:16:41,429 --> 00:16:42,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you see it?</font>

281
00:16:43,389 --> 00:16:45,859
<font color=#FFFF00>- I don't see anything. - Hey.</font>

282
00:16:46,429 --> 00:16:48,989
<font color=#FFFF00>You will see them once they are built.</font>

283
00:16:49,289 --> 00:16:52,389
<font color=#FFFF00>World-famous architects will design the buildings.</font>

284
00:16:52,389 --> 00:16:54,789
<font color=#FFFF00>The buildings will stand out.</font>

285
00:16:54,959 --> 00:16:57,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Han, you are here.</font>

286
00:16:57,529 --> 00:16:58,829
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't know you were here.</font>

287
00:16:58,859 --> 00:17:01,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course. We will start construction soon.</font>

288
00:17:01,829 --> 00:17:02,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

289
00:17:03,659 --> 00:17:05,929
<font color=#FFFF00>I came here with my wife.</font>

290
00:17:06,089 --> 00:17:07,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you?</font>

291
00:17:08,059 --> 00:17:10,499
<font color=#FFFF00>It's nice to meet you, ma'am.</font>

292
00:17:11,159 --> 00:17:12,829
<font color=#FFFF00>When will you start construction?</font>

293
00:17:12,959 --> 00:17:14,559
<font color=#FFFF00>We will start early next week.</font>

294
00:17:14,889 --> 00:17:17,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Take a look at this.</font>

295
00:17:17,159 --> 00:17:19,759
<font color=#FFFF00>As you can see, this is the main building.</font>

296
00:17:20,289 --> 00:17:22,929
<font color=#FFFF00>This is the aquarium.</font>

297
00:17:28,359 --> 00:17:30,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you sure you looked into it closely?</font>

298
00:17:31,129 --> 00:17:32,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo.</font>

299
00:17:33,589 --> 00:17:37,499
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel relieved at heart just by looking at the land.</font>

300
00:17:38,459 --> 00:17:39,999
<font color=#FFFF00>As a man,</font>

301
00:17:40,529 --> 00:17:42,929
<font color=#FFFF00>I should've had...</font>

302
00:17:43,289 --> 00:17:46,629
<font color=#FFFF00>a big dream just like this. Don't you think?</font>

303
00:17:46,959 --> 00:17:49,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you sure everything is okay?</font>

304
00:17:49,889 --> 00:17:51,389
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you think?</font>

305
00:17:51,789 --> 00:17:53,889
<font color=#FFFF00>They will start construction next week.</font>

306
00:17:55,189 --> 00:17:58,289
<font color=#FFFF00>So are you sure you checked the whole thing?</font>

307
00:17:58,999 --> 00:18:00,659
<font color=#FFFF00>- You are... - Hye Joo.</font>

308
00:18:00,999 --> 00:18:02,289
<font color=#FFFF00>There will be a light...</font>

309
00:18:02,629 --> 00:18:04,689
<font color=#FFFF00>at the end of the tunnel.</font>

310
00:18:18,559 --> 00:18:20,559
<font color=#FFFF00>(Inbox)</font>

311
00:18:24,789 --> 00:18:27,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Why isn't the sales report ready yet?</font>

312
00:18:28,129 --> 00:18:29,689
<font color=#FFFF00>It has never happened before.</font>

313
00:18:30,329 --> 00:18:33,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, Dong Hui was in charge of the work.</font>

314
00:18:35,589 --> 00:18:39,329
<font color=#FFFF00>So? Are you saying it's not ready because she's not here?</font>

315
00:18:39,829 --> 00:18:41,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you using her as an excuse?</font>

316
00:18:42,089 --> 00:18:44,229
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry. I will have it ready as soon as possible.</font>

317
00:18:54,959 --> 00:18:57,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello, Writer Choi. Did you get my message?</font>

318
00:18:57,359 --> 00:18:59,689
<font color=#FFFF00>I was too busy to give you a call.</font>

319
00:19:01,129 --> 00:19:02,589
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean you want to stay out of this?</font>

320
00:19:03,089 --> 00:19:06,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Writer Choi, please don't be upset.</font>

321
00:19:06,259 --> 00:19:09,089
<font color=#FFFF00>I understand it hurt your feelings.</font>

322
00:19:09,129 --> 00:19:11,229
<font color=#FFFF00>As you know, Oh Dong Hui is a novice writer.</font>

323
00:19:11,389 --> 00:19:14,529
<font color=#FFFF00>She won't be able to write well due to her lack of persistence.</font>

324
00:19:15,059 --> 00:19:17,789
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure she will give up writing soon.</font>

325
00:19:18,159 --> 00:19:19,189
<font color=#FFFF00>So please...</font>

326
00:19:19,929 --> 00:19:22,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Writer Choi! Writer Choi!</font>

327
00:19:24,659 --> 00:19:25,999
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe this.</font>

328
00:19:26,559 --> 00:19:28,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui is already fired.</font>

329
00:19:28,499 --> 00:19:30,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Who would write the script now?</font>

330
00:19:44,559 --> 00:19:47,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you run away just to be at a place like this?</font>

331
00:19:48,059 --> 00:19:51,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you know that Gui Boon ran away from my father?</font>

332
00:19:52,429 --> 00:19:54,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Gui Boon has a connection...</font>

333
00:19:55,529 --> 00:19:58,129
<font color=#FFFF00>with my grandmother who was the chairwoman.</font>

334
00:19:58,999 --> 00:20:01,859
<font color=#FFFF00>My father is looking for Gui Boon...</font>

335
00:20:02,059 --> 00:20:03,859
<font color=#FFFF00>to find my grandmother and her will.</font>

336
00:20:04,589 --> 00:20:05,729
<font color=#FFFF00>All I'm saying...</font>

337
00:20:06,229 --> 00:20:08,029
<font color=#FFFF00>is that you shouldn't trample...</font>

338
00:20:08,459 --> 00:20:10,629
<font color=#FFFF00>on her time and trouble to hide in a remote town...</font>

339
00:20:10,959 --> 00:20:13,529
<font color=#FFFF00>just because of your stupid love stuff.</font>

340
00:20:29,529 --> 00:20:30,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

341
00:20:30,929 --> 00:20:33,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you get caught by your grandmother again?</font>

342
00:20:34,059 --> 00:20:35,499
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't send me an email.</font>

343
00:20:35,499 --> 00:20:37,659
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't even read my email yet.</font>

344
00:20:39,029 --> 00:20:40,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Is everything all right?</font>

345
00:20:41,189 --> 00:20:42,289
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm worried.</font>

346
00:20:42,689 --> 00:20:44,259
<font color=#FFFF00>It's just too long...</font>

347
00:20:44,389 --> 00:20:46,089
<font color=#FFFF00>to wait until the weekend.</font>

348
00:20:47,859 --> 00:20:48,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Right.</font>

349
00:20:49,389 --> 00:20:52,459
<font color=#FFFF00>You nailed the scripts for episode 5 and 6 again.</font>

350
00:20:53,589 --> 00:20:55,329
<font color=#FFFF00>I want to celebrate it with you.</font>

351
00:21:00,499 --> 00:21:02,059
<font color=#FFFF00>(Your mail has been successfully sent.)</font>

352
00:21:11,389 --> 00:21:13,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Senior Secretary Kim, how are you?</font>

353
00:21:14,189 --> 00:21:15,689
<font color=#FFFF00>It's Han Seong Sik.</font>

354
00:21:16,029 --> 00:21:18,959
<font color=#FFFF00>How have you been?</font>

355
00:21:24,159 --> 00:21:26,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Senior Secretary Kim.</font>

356
00:21:26,429 --> 00:21:28,159
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you come here?</font>

357
00:21:28,259 --> 00:21:29,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

358
00:21:30,359 --> 00:21:32,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this to me?</font>

359
00:21:32,829 --> 00:21:34,829
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm just here to pay my respects to you.</font>

360
00:21:35,759 --> 00:21:36,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Your respects?</font>

361
00:21:37,789 --> 00:21:40,559
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you come here after doing such things?</font>

362
00:21:40,859 --> 00:21:41,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Why...</font>

363
00:21:42,229 --> 00:21:44,689
<font color=#FFFF00>are you upset? What did I do wrong?</font>

364
00:21:44,959 --> 00:21:47,189
<font color=#FFFF00>I just went to the prosecutor's office...</font>

365
00:21:47,529 --> 00:21:49,429
<font color=#FFFF00>and had seolleongtang. That's it.</font>

366
00:21:50,789 --> 00:21:52,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I had six bowls of seolleongtang.</font>

367
00:21:54,389 --> 00:21:56,589
<font color=#FFFF00>How could a small fry like you...</font>

368
00:21:56,859 --> 00:21:58,059
<font color=#FFFF00>work as a mole?</font>

369
00:21:59,459 --> 00:22:00,789
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

370
00:22:01,029 --> 00:22:02,859
<font color=#FFFF00>You and Lee Hyun Woo of Jinsung Daily News...</font>

371
00:22:03,059 --> 00:22:04,659
<font color=#FFFF00>revealed the relations...</font>

372
00:22:05,389 --> 00:22:07,329
<font color=#FFFF00>between Seonghan Group and Minjeong Party.</font>

373
00:22:07,329 --> 00:22:10,189
<font color=#FFFF00>What? What did you say?</font>

374
00:22:11,229 --> 00:22:14,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh. He said he'd get me...</font>

375
00:22:14,589 --> 00:22:16,429
<font color=#FFFF00>a smart and obedient guy as a scapegoat.</font>

376
00:22:16,929 --> 00:22:19,159
<font color=#FFFF00>- It was a dirty trick. - What?</font>

377
00:22:20,189 --> 00:22:22,329
<font color=#FFFF00>- A scapegoat? A dirty trick? - Shut your mouth.</font>

378
00:22:23,689 --> 00:22:25,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Hyun Woo of Jinsung Daily News...</font>

379
00:22:25,189 --> 00:22:27,289
<font color=#FFFF00>got me a stupid and loud guy like you...</font>

380
00:22:27,889 --> 00:22:28,929
<font color=#FFFF00>on purpose.</font>

381
00:22:29,029 --> 00:22:31,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Then he made me a fool...</font>

382
00:22:31,259 --> 00:22:33,289
<font color=#FFFF00>printing out the newspapers.</font>

383
00:22:33,389 --> 00:22:34,389
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

384
00:22:35,489 --> 00:22:37,459
<font color=#FFFF00>What exactly do you mean?</font>

385
00:22:38,359 --> 00:22:41,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you saying Lee Hyun Woo...</font>

386
00:22:41,789 --> 00:22:44,529
<font color=#FFFF00>used me as a scapegoat?</font>

387
00:22:44,829 --> 00:22:47,729
<font color=#FFFF00>To reveal the connection between you and Seonghan Group?</font>

388
00:22:50,089 --> 00:22:51,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Sik.</font>

389
00:22:51,989 --> 00:22:54,359
<font color=#FFFF00>There's not much to say about it.</font>

390
00:22:54,489 --> 00:22:56,689
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't let you set foot in this business again.</font>

391
00:22:57,729 --> 00:22:59,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't even think about...</font>

392
00:22:59,529 --> 00:23:02,689
<font color=#FFFF00>working in politics or broadcasting.</font>

393
00:23:03,289 --> 00:23:05,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Get out of my office now.</font>

394
00:23:07,029 --> 00:23:08,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Senior Secretary Kim.</font>

395
00:23:09,389 --> 00:23:10,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Senior Secretary Kim!</font>

396
00:23:20,489 --> 00:23:21,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you saying...</font>

397
00:23:22,589 --> 00:23:24,229
<font color=#FFFF00>I should drop the case...</font>

398
00:23:24,329 --> 00:23:25,729
<font color=#FFFF00>and settle my divorce?</font>

399
00:23:26,029 --> 00:23:28,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. They say you should do that...</font>

400
00:23:28,029 --> 00:23:29,829
<font color=#FFFF00>if you want to take your child.</font>

401
00:23:30,129 --> 00:23:33,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? Why do you think I stayed married to him for seven years?</font>

402
00:23:33,829 --> 00:23:36,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Why should I step back without getting a penny?</font>

403
00:23:36,859 --> 00:23:38,729
<font color=#FFFF00>This isn't fair.</font>

404
00:23:39,129 --> 00:23:41,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't cheat on him.</font>

405
00:23:41,189 --> 00:23:43,629
<font color=#FFFF00>It's hard to prove your innocence about the photos.</font>

406
00:23:44,089 --> 00:23:46,289
<font color=#FFFF00>They say Jinsung Daily News who spread the photos...</font>

407
00:23:46,359 --> 00:23:48,659
<font color=#FFFF00>passed the information to James Jeong.</font>

408
00:23:49,789 --> 00:23:51,689
<font color=#FFFF00>The photos were taken...</font>

409
00:23:52,789 --> 00:23:54,829
<font color=#FFFF00>to catch you having an affair.</font>

410
00:23:55,489 --> 00:23:58,189
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you say? Jinsung Daily News?</font>

411
00:24:00,489 --> 00:24:03,629
<font color=#FFFF00>My older brother used to work there.</font>

412
00:24:04,389 --> 00:24:05,929
