<font color=#FFFF00>are you asking why I didn't do anything to...</font>

620
00:34:11,689 --> 00:34:13,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Sik, whom you call your brother,</font>

621
00:34:14,529 --> 00:34:17,359
<font color=#FFFF00>when he tried to have a go at me?</font>

622
00:34:17,959 --> 00:34:19,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Those people...</font>

623
00:34:20,159 --> 00:34:22,129
<font color=#FFFF00>don't know anything.</font>

624
00:34:26,929 --> 00:34:28,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Since what happened yesterday,</font>

625
00:34:28,629 --> 00:34:30,129
<font color=#FFFF00>did you worry about me at all?</font>

626
00:34:31,029 --> 00:34:32,989
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't get a wink of sleep.</font>

627
00:34:37,259 --> 00:34:39,159
<font color=#FFFF00>You ran into my house...</font>

628
00:34:39,589 --> 00:34:42,289
<font color=#FFFF00>and ask me why I did that to them...</font>

629
00:34:42,899 --> 00:34:45,729
<font color=#FFFF00>instead of asking about the pain I've suffered from.</font>

630
00:34:47,959 --> 00:34:48,989
<font color=#FFFF00>I knew...</font>

631
00:34:50,089 --> 00:34:52,029
<font color=#FFFF00>things would turn out as Hyung Seop wanted.</font>

632
00:34:53,529 --> 00:34:56,729
<font color=#FFFF00>I know his sins cannot be forgiven by any means.</font>

633
00:34:57,329 --> 00:34:58,829
<font color=#FFFF00>But it's not their fault.</font>

634
00:34:58,989 --> 00:35:00,859
<font color=#FFFF00>They just sat back...</font>

635
00:35:00,859 --> 00:35:03,029
<font color=#FFFF00>and received everything from their parents.</font>

636
00:35:04,289 --> 00:35:06,399
<font color=#FFFF00>As they're driven into a corner,</font>

637
00:35:06,859 --> 00:35:08,159
<font color=#FFFF00>they tried to rip off a wealthy guy...</font>

638
00:35:08,359 --> 00:35:11,559
<font color=#FFFF00>living across the street only to ruin themselves.</font>

639
00:35:12,089 --> 00:35:13,459
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what they have done.</font>

640
00:35:13,759 --> 00:35:16,159
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hyun Woo. - How could you yell...</font>

641
00:35:16,459 --> 00:35:19,359
<font color=#FFFF00>and even swear at me as soon as you get here?</font>

642
00:35:21,329 --> 00:35:22,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Isn't this ridiculous?</font>

643
00:35:26,229 --> 00:35:27,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Am I to blame?</font>

644
00:35:28,289 --> 00:35:29,289
<font color=#FFFF00>No,</font>

645
00:35:29,899 --> 00:35:31,359
<font color=#FFFF00>this is just the way the world is.</font>

646
00:35:32,129 --> 00:35:34,159
<font color=#FFFF00>They should blame their parents who spoiled them.</font>

647
00:35:37,589 --> 00:35:40,859
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why they still live with their fully-grown children...</font>

648
00:35:41,629 --> 00:35:43,489
<font color=#FFFF00>justifying themselves that that's what parents do.</font>

649
00:35:44,629 --> 00:35:46,589
<font color=#FFFF00>I could become an independent person...</font>

650
00:35:48,029 --> 00:35:49,829
<font color=#FFFF00>because I lost my father when I was little.</font>

651
00:35:51,529 --> 00:35:54,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't make such sarcastic remarks.</font>

652
00:35:55,029 --> 00:35:56,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Then you're no different from my dad.</font>

653
00:36:00,329 --> 00:36:01,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Please stop, Hyun Woo.</font>

654
00:36:02,529 --> 00:36:03,759
<font color=#FFFF00>This is enough.</font>

655
00:36:06,989 --> 00:36:09,329
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sang Woo. - Let me...</font>

656
00:36:10,189 --> 00:36:11,559
<font color=#FFFF00>take care of the rest.</font>

657
00:36:12,359 --> 00:36:13,689
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll make sure...</font>

658
00:36:13,729 --> 00:36:15,989
<font color=#FFFF00>no one gets hurt because of this.</font>

659
00:36:17,529 --> 00:36:18,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Then I'll go to you.</font>

660
00:36:19,129 --> 00:36:20,159
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

661
00:36:21,089 --> 00:36:22,459
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure you can't do that.</font>

662
00:36:25,859 --> 00:36:28,459
<font color=#FFFF00>I've been watching you for quite a long time.</font>

663
00:36:29,589 --> 00:36:30,729
<font color=#FFFF00>You can never...</font>

664
00:36:32,059 --> 00:36:33,689
<font color=#FFFF00>put an end to all this on your own.</font>

665
00:36:34,329 --> 00:36:36,829
<font color=#FFFF00>You're wrong. I can.</font>

666
00:36:37,489 --> 00:36:38,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you sure?</font>

667
00:36:39,329 --> 00:36:41,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I can.</font>

668
00:36:43,989 --> 00:36:44,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Fine.</font>

669
00:36:45,629 --> 00:36:47,229
<font color=#FFFF00>If you say so,</font>

670
00:36:48,329 --> 00:36:49,529
<font color=#FFFF00>I need you to move out right away.</font>

671
00:36:51,129 --> 00:36:53,329
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll stop everything as you said.</font>

672
00:36:54,689 --> 00:36:57,059
<font color=#FFFF00>So disconnect all your ties with that family.</font>

673
00:37:03,089 --> 00:37:04,729
<font color=#FFFF00>You know we have an appointment tomorrow, right?</font>

674
00:37:05,759 --> 00:37:07,789
<font color=#FFFF00>The officials from the Golden Street headquarters are in Korea.</font>

675
00:37:08,689 --> 00:37:09,689
<font color=#FFFF00>I want...</font>

676
00:37:10,559 --> 00:37:12,029
<font color=#FFFF00>to show them my brother.</font>

677
00:37:13,129 --> 00:37:14,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Come with me.</font>

678
00:37:22,959 --> 00:37:24,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Make sure to dress up.</font>

679
00:37:25,159 --> 00:37:26,189
<font color=#FFFF00>I think...</font>

680
00:37:27,189 --> 00:37:28,559
<font color=#FFFF00>you're more good looking than me.</font>

681
00:37:29,289 --> 00:37:30,759
<font color=#FFFF00>That makes me the happiest.</font>

682
00:38:17,029 --> 00:38:18,059
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

683
00:38:21,729 --> 00:38:23,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui?</font>

684
00:38:23,589 --> 00:38:25,329
<font color=#FFFF00>You're back, Grandmother.</font>

685
00:38:25,559 --> 00:38:28,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you so absent-minded? How could you not notice me?</font>

686
00:38:28,989 --> 00:38:30,959
<font color=#FFFF00>I was thinking about something.</font>

687
00:38:31,189 --> 00:38:33,759
<font color=#FFFF00>What were you thinking about?</font>

688
00:38:34,989 --> 00:38:36,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you have dinner?</font>

689
00:38:36,489 --> 00:38:38,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Not yet. What about you?</font>

690
00:38:38,899 --> 00:38:40,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me make dinner for you.</font>

691
00:38:40,659 --> 00:38:43,259
<font color=#FFFF00>It's all right. I'm not hungry now.</font>

692
00:38:43,759 --> 00:38:46,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Why didn't you have dinner?</font>

693
00:38:46,729 --> 00:38:50,559
<font color=#FFFF00>You must not skip meals like that. You're still young.</font>

694
00:38:50,589 --> 00:38:52,489
<font color=#FFFF00>I've had some snacks.</font>

695
00:38:53,089 --> 00:38:55,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Aren't you cold?</font>

696
00:38:57,029 --> 00:38:58,359
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm fine.</font>

697
00:38:58,629 --> 00:39:01,989
<font color=#FFFF00>It doesn't really matter for old people like me.</font>

698
00:39:02,259 --> 00:39:03,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Please don't say that.</font>

699
00:39:06,589 --> 00:39:08,159
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you do today?</font>

700
00:39:09,359 --> 00:39:10,729
<font color=#FFFF00>I did nothing special.</font>

701
00:39:12,029 --> 00:39:13,589
<font color=#FFFF00>You stayed in all day long?</font>

702
00:39:14,329 --> 00:39:16,259
<font color=#FFFF00>What else could I do?</font>

703
00:39:16,429 --> 00:39:18,559
<font color=#FFFF00>You told me not to go outside.</font>

704
00:39:22,589 --> 00:39:24,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Wasn't it hard to just stay in?</font>

705
00:39:24,559 --> 00:39:26,159
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm all right.</font>

706
00:39:26,459 --> 00:39:29,259
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't go many places when I lived in Seoul either.</font>

707
00:39:29,429 --> 00:39:31,959
<font color=#FFFF00>I just went to work and came home every day.</font>

708
00:39:33,759 --> 00:39:35,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. I'm relieved then.</font>

709
00:39:36,229 --> 00:39:37,529
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm glad to hear that.</font>

710
00:39:39,399 --> 00:39:40,489
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way,</font>

711
00:39:41,129 --> 00:39:43,429
<font color=#FFFF00>I have something to ask you.</font>

712
00:39:44,659 --> 00:39:45,659
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it?</font>

713
00:39:46,959 --> 00:39:49,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you have to move this far?</font>

714
00:39:51,899 --> 00:39:52,899
<font color=#FFFF00>I just wondered...</font>

715
00:39:53,059 --> 00:39:56,759
<font color=#FFFF00>if there was some reason why we had to move to this remote town.</font>

716
00:39:57,929 --> 00:39:59,229
<font color=#FFFF00>There's no reason.</font>

717
00:39:59,829 --> 00:40:01,189
<font color=#FFFF00>I just wanted...</font>

718
00:40:01,989 --> 00:40:04,089
<font color=#FFFF00>to lead a quiet life with you.</font>

719
00:40:05,589 --> 00:40:06,689
<font color=#FFFF00>But...</font>

720
00:40:08,029 --> 00:40:10,559
<font color=#FFFF00>there's something I am curious about.</font>

721
00:40:13,529 --> 00:40:16,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you have any trouble with President Bang?</font>

722
00:40:17,859 --> 00:40:21,129
<font color=#FFFF00>What... What on earth are you talking about?</font>

723
00:40:21,259 --> 00:40:22,489
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean by trouble?</font>

724
00:40:23,089 --> 00:40:25,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Why would I have any trouble with him?</font>

725
00:40:26,959 --> 00:40:28,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Forget it.</font>

726
00:40:28,659 --> 00:40:31,829
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought President Bang cared a lot about you,</font>

727
00:40:32,029 --> 00:40:34,629
<font color=#FFFF00>but you didn't even call him before we moved here.</font>

728
00:40:34,729 --> 00:40:36,259
<font color=#FFFF00>So I wondered if something happened.</font>

729
00:40:36,659 --> 00:40:39,089
<font color=#FFFF00>I was just curious. That's it.</font>

730
00:40:39,459 --> 00:40:41,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

731
00:40:41,789 --> 00:40:45,729
<font color=#FFFF00>I also love living with you alone.</font>

732
00:40:45,929 --> 00:40:47,429
<font color=#FFFF00>I really mean it.</font>

733
00:41:20,929 --> 00:41:21,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

734
00:41:22,899 --> 00:41:25,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes?</font>

735
00:41:26,429 --> 00:41:28,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you still up?</font>

736
00:41:28,559 --> 00:41:29,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you ill?</font>

737
00:41:30,929 --> 00:41:32,189
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm okay.</font>

738
00:41:33,399 --> 00:41:34,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

739
00:41:36,189 --> 00:41:37,959
<font color=#FFFF00>I just can't fall asleep easily.</font>

740
00:41:38,589 --> 00:41:41,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Old people all have trouble falling asleep. You'll know later.</font>

741
00:41:43,189 --> 00:41:44,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Were you crying?</font>

742
00:41:45,489 --> 00:41:48,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, a little.</font>

743
00:41:49,689 --> 00:41:50,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Why?</font>

744
00:41:52,229 --> 00:41:53,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Because I couldn't fall asleep.</font>

745
00:41:55,259 --> 00:41:58,959
<font color=#FFFF00>I just couldn't help thinking about various things.</font>

746
00:42:00,529 --> 00:42:01,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother...</font>

747
00:42:07,189 --> 00:42:09,229
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel bad for you.</font>

748
00:42:10,399 --> 00:42:12,529
<font color=#FFFF00>You're suffering a lot...</font>

749
00:42:12,529 --> 00:42:14,229
<font color=#FFFF00>because I took you here with me.</font>

750
00:42:14,829 --> 00:42:15,829
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I cried.</font>

751
00:42:16,329 --> 00:42:17,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry.</font>

752
00:42:17,659 --> 00:42:20,189
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you I like it here.</font>

753
00:42:20,759 --> 00:42:23,259
<font color=#FFFF00>It's quiet, so I can write the scripts better.</font>

754
00:42:23,529 --> 00:42:26,729
<font color=#FFFF00>It's also comfortable to live with you alone.</font>

755
00:42:29,859 --> 00:42:32,989
<font color=#FFFF00>You're not meant to suffer in this remote place.</font>

756
00:42:34,029 --> 00:42:35,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry?</font>

757
00:42:36,159 --> 00:42:37,589
<font color=#FFFF00>You should have been...</font>

758
00:42:38,359 --> 00:42:40,459
<font color=#FFFF00>raised in a wealthy family and received a lot of love.</font>

759
00:42:40,929 --> 00:42:43,159
<font color=#FFFF00>You should have lived in a happy family.</font>

760
00:42:44,589 --> 00:42:45,859
<font color=#FFFF00>You're going through a lot...</font>

761
00:42:47,329 --> 00:42:49,229
<font color=#FFFF00>because of me.</font>

762
00:42:50,589 --> 00:42:52,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

763
00:42:54,589 --> 00:42:55,859
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

764
00:42:57,859 --> 00:42:59,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I am really sorry.</font>

765
00:43:01,329 --> 00:43:03,959
<font color=#FFFF00>I will pay a heavy price...</font>

766
00:43:04,459 --> 00:43:07,129
<font color=#FFFF00>later.</font>

767
00:43:09,559 --> 00:43:10,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Come here.</font>

768
00:43:12,529 --> 00:43:14,059
<font color=#FFFF00>My Dong Hui.</font>

769
00:43:14,559 --> 00:43:16,789
<font color=#FFFF00>My poor girl.</font>

770
00:43:18,729 --> 00:43:19,859
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

771
00:43:21,659 --> 00:43:22,729
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry.</font>

772
00:43:27,629 --> 00:43:28,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother.</font>

773
00:43:32,559 --> 00:43:34,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you here so early today?</font>

774
00:43:34,259 --> 00:43:35,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo isn't here yet.</font>

775
00:43:35,989 --> 00:43:38,189
<font color=#FFFF00>You know I left 10 minutes earlier last time.</font>

776
00:43:38,189 --> 00:43:39,899
<font color=#FFFF00>So I came early today.</font>

777
00:43:40,399 --> 00:43:41,959
<font color=#FFFF00>This is for you.</font>

778
00:43:45,089 --> 00:43:48,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you here to play around?</font>

779
00:43:48,159 --> 00:43:49,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course.</font>

780
00:43:49,729 --> 00:43:51,129
<font color=#FFFF00>This is where my romance is played.</font>

781
00:43:53,189 --> 00:43:55,229
<font color=#FFFF00>My goodness. That's lame.</font>

782
00:43:55,989 --> 00:43:58,729
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll stay in my room. Leave when the lesson is over.</font>

783
00:43:58,829 --> 00:44:01,829
<font color=#FFFF00>And I'll throw these flowers away when you leave.</font>

784
00:44:02,159 --> 00:44:03,589
<font color=#FFFF00>I think it's too rude...</font>

785
00:44:03,589 --> 00:44:05,929
<font color=#FFFF00>to throw them away in front of you.</font>

786
00:44:09,989 --> 00:44:10,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Start the music.</font>

787
00:44:15,859 --> 00:44:18,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Beautiful Dreamer,</font>

788
00:44:18,329 --> 00:44:22,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Wake unto me</font>

789
00:44:22,589 --> 00:44:25,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Starlight and dewdrops are</font>

790
00:44:25,189 --> 00:44:27,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Waiting for thee</font>

791
00:44:29,089 --> 00:44:32,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Sounds of the rude world</font>

792
00:44:32,559 --> 00:44:35,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Past the sun</font>

793
00:44:35,559 --> 00:44:40,959
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel empty inside</font>

794
00:44:42,559 --> 00:44:48,559
<font color=#FFFF00>You are a cute pal in my dream</font>

795
00:44:48,789 --> 00:44:51,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Listen to me</font>

796
00:44:51,329 --> 00:44:57,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Listen to my beautiful song</font>

797
00:44:59,129 --> 00:45:00,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, Mom?</font>

798
00:45:01,259 --> 00:45:03,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing's going on at your house, right?</font>

799
00:45:03,529 --> 00:45:05,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing's going on.</font>

800
00:45:06,289 --> 00:45:07,659
<font color=#FFFF00>What, Mom?</font>

801
00:45:07,789 --> 00:45:10,459
<font color=#FFFF00>My ears are working fine. Why are you yelling at me?</font>

802
00:45:10,989 --> 00:45:13,789
<font color=#FFFF00>What is this? Is someone singing?</font>

803
00:45:13,789 --> 00:45:15,829
<font color=#FFFF00>I mean... Mom.</font>

804
00:45:15,829 --> 00:45:18,129
<font color=#FFFF00>I turned up the volume today.</font>

805
00:45:18,459 --> 00:45:20,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. That jerk.</font>

806
00:45:20,759 --> 00:45:22,789
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, what's up?</font>

807
00:45:22,989 --> 00:45:24,789
<font color=#FFFF00>You know what?</font>

808
00:45:25,089 --> 00:45:28,289
<font color=#FFFF00>I found out Mr. Lee across the street bullied our grandchildren.</font>

809
00:45:28,389 --> 00:45:29,459
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

810
00:45:30,059 --> 00:45:32,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom. What do you mean?</font>

811
00:45:35,089 --> 00:45:38,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Please wake up</font>

812
00:45:38,629 --> 00:45:40,329
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't let her off easy this time.</font>

813
00:45:45,259 --> 00:45:46,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey. Jeong Eun.</font>

814
00:45:46,959 --> 00:45:48,059
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

815
00:45:48,059 --> 00:45:49,359
<font color=#FFFF00>What is this mess?</font>

816
00:45:49,659 --> 00:45:50,759
<font color=#FFFF00>What mess?</font>

817
00:45:50,959 --> 00:45:53,029
<font color=#FFFF00>The man you used to date.</font>

818
00:45:53,029 --> 00:45:54,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Hyun Woo across the street.</font>

819
00:45:54,529 --> 00:45:56,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it true that he came back...</font>

820
00:45:56,129 --> 00:45:58,329
<font color=#FFFF00>here to take revenge on your uncle?</font>

821
00:45:58,959 --> 00:46:00,889
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not true. Mom.</font>

822
00:46:00,889 --> 00:46:03,759
<font color=#FFFF00>If it's not, why did your grandmother call me to say this?</font>

823
00:46:03,859 --> 00:46:05,259
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not what happened.</font>

824
00:46:05,259 --> 00:46:07,189
<font color=#FFFF00>He had his reasons.</font>

825
00:46:07,189 --> 00:46:09,659
<font color=#FFFF00>How can such a vicious guy have reasons?</font>

826
00:46:10,529 --> 00:46:13,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that why he approached you on purpose?</font>

827
00:46:13,559 --> 00:46:16,189
<font color=#FFFF00>No, Mom. He didn't do anything wrong to me.</font>

828
00:46:16,189 --> 00:46:18,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you see that he used you?</font>

829
00:46:18,789 --> 00:46:21,259
<font color=#FFFF00>This is why he played you and then left you.</font>

830
00:46:21,259 --> 00:46:24,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Because of him, you cried day and night and suffered.</font>

831
00:46:24,129 --> 00:46:26,359
<font color=#FFFF00>That is not how it happened, Mom.</font>

832
00:46:26,359 --> 00:46:28,829
<font color=#FFFF00>You are pathetic.</font>

833
00:46:28,829 --> 00:46:30,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Today will be the last day for both of us.</font>

834
00:46:30,789 --> 00:46:32,329
<font color=#FFFF00>What did I tell you?</font>

835
00:46:32,329 --> 00:46:34,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Didn't I tell you to be careful of men?</font>

836
00:46:35,459 --> 00:46:36,759
<font color=#FFFF00>You learned what I told you not to learn...</font>

837
00:46:36,759 --> 00:46:38,689
<font color=#FFFF00>and didn't learn what you should've learned.</font>

838
00:46:38,689 --> 00:46:40,889
<font color=#FFFF00>I am going to cut off all of your hair today.</font>

839
00:46:40,889 --> 00:46:42,529
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hey. Ae Ri. - Come here.</font>

840
00:46:42,529 --> 00:46:44,529
<font color=#FFFF00>- Come here. - This is beneath you.</font>

841
00:46:44,529 --> 00:46:45,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop hurting my daughter.</font>

842
00:46:45,929 --> 00:46:48,429
<font color=#FFFF00>What? Your daughter? Did you say "my daughter"?</font>

843
00:46:48,429 --> 00:46:50,389
<font color=#FFFF00>You resurfaced after 30 years.</font>

844
00:46:50,389 --> 00:46:53,359
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you pretend to be her father? Stay out of it.</font>

845
00:46:53,529 --> 00:46:55,429
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mom. - Today,</font>

846
00:46:55,429 --> 00:46:57,359
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dad, are you okay? - I'm going to...</font>

847
00:46:57,859 --> 00:46:59,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I am not okay.</font>

848
00:46:59,589 --> 00:47:01,629
<font color=#FFFF00>What is this? You got zero?</font>

849
00:47:01,759 --> 00:47:03,059
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you score zero?</font>

850
00:47:03,789 --> 00:47:06,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo. I am scared.</font>

851
00:47:06,789 --> 00:47:08,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah In. Don't worry. I'm here.</font>

852
00:47:09,559 --> 00:47:13,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think I know you did this on purpose?</font>

853
00:47:15,789 --> 00:47:17,689
<font color=#FFFF00>There is not a day that goes by peacefully.</font>

854
00:47:18,959 --> 00:47:22,089
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way, Mom is feeling under the weather. What should I do?</font>

855
00:47:22,489 --> 00:47:25,489
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with you? You had your fun.</font>

856
00:47:25,489 --> 00:47:27,659
<font color=#FFFF00>It's time for you to pull yourself together and study.</font>

857
00:47:27,789 --> 00:47:29,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you still rebelling?</font>

858
00:47:29,429 --> 00:47:31,259
<font color=#FFFF00>So you should stop already!</font>

859
00:47:32,289 --> 00:47:33,989
<font color=#FFFF00>I can study...</font>

860
00:47:34,289 --> 00:47:36,129
<font color=#FFFF00>without you nagging me.</font>

861
00:47:36,129 --> 00:47:37,429
<font color=#FFFF00>How can your rank drop like this...</font>

862
00:47:37,489 --> 00:47:39,389
<font color=#FFFF00>if you can study by yourself?</font>

863
00:47:39,689 --> 00:47:41,129
<font color=#FFFF00>The result speaks for itself!</font>

864
00:47:42,259 --> 00:47:43,589
<font color=#FFFF00>My mom said it would be enough for her...</font>

865
00:47:43,759 --> 00:47:46,329
<font color=#FFFF00>as long as I am ranked within the 10th place.</font>

866
00:47:48,159 --> 00:47:49,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this to me, Aunt?</font>

867
00:47:50,959 --> 00:47:52,259
<font color=#FFFF00>If you study just a bit,</font>

868
00:47:52,359 --> 00:47:54,789
<font color=#FFFF00>you can be top of your class.</font>

869
00:47:54,789 --> 00:47:57,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you satisfied with just a 10th place?</font>

870
00:47:58,289 --> 00:48:01,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you realize anything from watching what happened to us?</font>

871
00:48:01,859 --> 00:48:04,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if you pass the bar exam, become a reporter,</font>

872
00:48:04,029 --> 00:48:05,529
<font color=#FFFF00>or graduate from the most prestigious university,</font>

873
00:48:05,689 --> 00:48:08,189
<font color=#FFFF00>it's nothing unless you are the best.</font>

874
00:48:08,429 --> 00:48:10,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Can't you realize it after seeing what happened to our family?</font>

875
00:48:11,229 --> 00:48:14,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Aunt. That's all you see.</font>

876
00:48:14,959 --> 00:48:17,459
<font color=#FFFF00>All of my parents studied hard.</font>

877
00:48:17,889 --> 00:48:19,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Have you ever wondered...</font>

878
00:48:20,829 --> 00:48:22,359
<font color=#FFFF00>if they are happy now?</font>

879
00:48:22,859 --> 00:48:26,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. Listen to yourself.</font>

880
00:48:26,959 --> 00:48:28,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Who said we are not happy?</font>

881
00:48:29,389 --> 00:48:32,089
<font color=#FFFF00>We are happy. We are very happy.</font>

882
00:48:33,529 --> 00:48:36,829
<font color=#FFFF00>If you want to be happy like us, you can start by studying.</font>

883
00:48:37,729 --> 00:48:40,089
<font color=#FFFF00>If a smart boy like you doesn't study,</font>

884
00:48:40,089 --> 00:48:41,889
<font color=#FFFF00>who would study?</font>

885
00:48:41,889 --> 00:48:44,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon. Let's not give up. Please?</font>

886
00:48:46,629 --> 00:48:48,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Chang Soo. Take your mother away.</font>

887
00:48:49,189 --> 00:48:50,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

888
00:48:50,389 --> 00:48:51,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon. Please.</font>

889
00:48:52,129 --> 00:48:54,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. What are you doing?</font>

890
00:48:54,789 --> 00:48:56,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Didn't you go to your lesson?</font>

891
00:48:56,389 --> 00:48:58,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Escort her upstairs.</font>

892
00:48:58,729 --> 00:49:01,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go, Mom. You're not feeling good. Why don't you rest?</font>

893
00:49:01,929 --> 00:49:02,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Hold on.</font>

894
00:49:03,189 --> 00:49:05,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me off. Put me down. Chang Soo.</font>

895
00:49:05,989 --> 00:49:08,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon. You can be happy.</font>

896
00:49:12,759 --> 00:49:13,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon.</font>

897
00:49:15,289 --> 00:49:16,959
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel like she will suffocate me to death.</font>

898
00:49:18,059 --> 00:49:19,359
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't breathe.</font>

899
00:49:24,189 --> 00:49:25,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon.</font>

900
00:49:27,589 --> 00:49:29,789
<font color=#FFFF00>It's really hard for me.</font>

901
00:49:30,459 --> 00:49:31,929
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't live in this house.</font>

902
00:49:34,289 --> 00:49:35,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon.</font>

903
00:49:36,059 --> 00:49:37,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Your former mother...</font>

904
00:49:38,229 --> 00:49:40,429
<font color=#FFFF00>raised you for a long time.</font>

905
00:49:41,289 --> 00:49:44,759
<font color=#FFFF00>She thinks you are still her son.</font>

906
00:49:46,229 --> 00:49:48,029
<font color=#FFFF00>She hasn't regained her senses yet.</font>

907
00:49:49,589 --> 00:49:50,689
<font color=#FFFF00>So Ji Hoon,</font>

908
00:49:51,159 --> 00:49:53,789
<font color=#FFFF00>while you live here,</font>

909
00:49:54,089 --> 00:49:57,059
<font color=#FFFF00>don't argue with her.</font>

910
00:49:57,059 --> 00:50:00,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Just let her have her ways sometimes. Okay?</font>

911
00:50:01,659 --> 00:50:04,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Ji Hoon. Wait a bit more.</font>

912
00:50:04,959 --> 00:50:07,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom and Dad are trying right now.</font>

913
00:50:07,929 --> 00:50:10,129
<font color=#FFFF00>We are going to move out soon.</font>

914
00:50:10,829 --> 00:50:12,089
<font color=#FFFF00>If she keeps at it,</font>

915
00:50:13,289 --> 00:50:16,289
<font color=#FFFF00>there's no point for me to live in the basement giving up...</font>

916
00:50:16,289 --> 00:50:18,259
<font color=#FFFF00>my room and comfortable life.</font>

917
00:50:19,159 --> 00:50:20,229
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

918
00:50:20,389 --> 00:50:22,589
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't come down because I wanted.</font>

919
00:50:23,289 --> 00:50:25,189
<font color=#FFFF00>I came down here...</font>

920
00:50:25,559 --> 00:50:27,429
<font color=#FFFF00>because living upstairs was a torture.</font>

921
00:50:28,729 --> 00:50:30,129
<font color=#FFFF00>She even followed me here.</font>

922
00:50:32,629 --> 00:50:34,289
<font color=#FFFF00>She's trying to kill me.</font>

923
00:50:37,129 --> 00:50:39,929
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

924
00:50:41,829 --> 00:50:45,359
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean there's no point?</font>

925
00:50:46,229 --> 00:50:47,859
<font color=#FFFF00>You...</font>

926
00:50:48,289 --> 00:50:52,329
<font color=#FFFF00>came down because of your biological mother and father.</font>

927
00:50:53,659 --> 00:50:55,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Whatever.</font>

928
00:51:01,329 --> 00:51:03,459
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't sleep a wink last night.</font>

929
00:51:03,989 --> 00:51:06,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think he's sly no matter how you look at this?</font>

930
00:51:06,829 --> 00:51:09,629
<font color=#FFFF00>That's my point. I am dumbfounded. This is so shocking.</font>

931
00:51:09,629 --> 00:51:11,789
<font color=#FFFF00>I still don't feel at ease.</font>

932
00:51:12,029 --> 00:51:13,429
<font color=#FFFF00>I knew it.</font>

933
00:51:13,829 --> 00:51:15,529
<font color=#FFFF00>He made a small scratch on my car,</font>

934
00:51:15,529 --> 00:51:18,029
<font color=#FFFF00>but he lent me an expensive car.</font>

935
00:51:18,059 --> 00:51:20,489
<font color=#FFFF00>He let me rent an office at a low rate.</font>

936
00:51:20,759 --> 00:51:23,859
<font color=#FFFF00>How could I have thought that he did those out of kindness?</font>

937
00:51:24,289 --> 00:51:27,159
<font color=#FFFF00>I still have... Mom. Look.</font>

938
00:51:27,159 --> 00:51:29,289
<font color=#FFFF00>I still have goosebumps.</font>

939
00:51:32,829 --> 00:51:35,159
<font color=#FFFF00>How can he do this with such a gentle face?</font>

940
00:51:35,389 --> 00:51:36,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Exactly.</font>

941
00:51:37,059 --> 00:51:40,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I still remember the day he moved into the neighborhood.</font>

942
00:51:41,189 --> 00:51:43,959
<font color=#FFFF00>The thought of it makes me shiver.</font>

943
00:51:43,989 --> 00:51:45,759
<font color=#FFFF00>He treated us so well.</font>

944
00:51:45,759 --> 00:51:47,489
<font color=#FFFF00>We treated him just as well as he did.</font>

945
00:51:48,159 --> 00:51:49,929
<font color=#FFFF00>But how could he have...</font>

946
00:51:49,929 --> 00:51:51,529
<font color=#FFFF00>such a vicious ulterior motive...</font>

947
00:51:51,529 --> 00:51:53,359
<font color=#FFFF00>and befriend us?</font>

948
00:51:53,459 --> 00:51:55,729
<font color=#FFFF00>The thought of it gives me goosebumps.</font>

949
00:51:56,229 --> 00:51:57,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Crazy jerk.</font>

950
00:51:57,629 --> 00:52:00,659
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a psychopath. He's out of his mind.</font>

951
00:52:01,529 --> 00:52:03,029
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa.</font>

952
00:52:03,159 --> 00:52:04,729
<font color=#FFFF00>It's true.</font>

953
00:52:04,729 --> 00:52:07,959
<font color=#FFFF00>To be honest, how can his father's suicide be your fault?</font>

954
00:52:08,259 --> 00:52:10,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did he commit suicide leaving his children behind?</font>

955
00:52:10,289 --> 00:52:12,459
<font color=#FFFF00>He should have raised them after paying for what he did.</font>

956
00:52:12,789 --> 00:52:15,689
<font color=#FFFF00>If I were him, I wouldn't be able to get rid of my daughter's face...</font>

957
00:52:15,689 --> 00:52:17,289
<font color=#FFFF00>until the moment I died.</font>

958
00:52:17,459 --> 00:52:18,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it.</font>

959
00:52:19,629 --> 00:52:21,829
<font color=#FFFF00>This is all my fault.</font>

960
00:52:22,029 --> 00:52:24,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Why is it your fault?</font>

961
00:52:24,629 --> 00:52:26,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you kill that bus driver?</font>

962
00:52:26,959 --> 00:52:28,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you help him hang himself?</font>

963
00:52:28,629 --> 00:52:30,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Or did you hold him up to hang himself?</font>

964
00:52:30,829 --> 00:52:32,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey.</font>

965
00:52:32,459 --> 00:52:35,529
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm pointing out the facts. At that time, a lot of children were hurt.</font>

966
00:52:35,529 --> 00:52:37,489
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Hwa almost died from the accident.</font>

967
00:52:37,689 --> 00:52:40,559
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you have stayed on the sideline when she was about to die?</font>

968
00:52:40,929 --> 00:52:43,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Besides, he drove under the influence.</font>

969
00:52:44,189 --> 00:52:46,389
<font color=#FFFF00>You just called him an alcoholic because he was one.</font>

970
00:52:46,429 --> 00:52:50,089
<font color=#FFFF00>You filed a report to the police. You didn't do anything wrong.</font>

971
00:52:50,929 --> 00:52:53,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that why he committed suicide?</font>

972
00:52:56,389 --> 00:52:59,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. It is a sad story indeed.</font>

973
00:52:59,059 --> 00:53:02,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Grandmother. It has nothing to do with us.</font>

974
00:53:02,429 --> 00:53:05,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Drinking and driving is a habit for people like him.</font>

975
00:53:05,459 --> 00:53:07,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if he didn't get caught that time,</font>

976
00:53:07,389 --> 00:53:09,289
<font color=#FFFF00>he would have definitely driven after drinking.</font>

977
00:53:09,289 --> 00:53:11,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Then other children might have been hurt too.</font>

978
00:53:12,029 --> 00:53:14,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Enough is enough.</font>

979
00:53:14,129 --> 00:53:16,429
<font color=#FFFF00>You, stay out of it.</font>

980
00:53:17,189 --> 00:53:18,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Is this why...</font>

981
00:53:19,289 --> 00:53:22,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee grabbed you by the collar?</font>

982
00:53:23,029 --> 00:53:26,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Eun should have kept her mouth shut.</font>

983
00:53:26,629 --> 00:53:28,129
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe her too.</font>

984
00:53:28,129 --> 00:53:30,329
<font color=#FFFF00>If she knew about this, she should've told us sooner.</font>

985
00:53:30,329 --> 00:53:32,789
<font color=#FFFF00>How can she keep this a secret from us?</font>

986
00:53:32,789 --> 00:53:35,029
<font color=#FFFF00>What if Mr. Lee did manage to ruin our family?</font>

987
00:53:35,029 --> 00:53:36,359
<font color=#FFFF00>What would she have done then?</font>

988
00:53:36,389 --> 00:53:38,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh. She's ridiculous.</font>

989
00:53:38,659 --> 00:53:40,159
<font color=#FFFF00>She'd better not show her face here.</font>

990
00:53:40,359 --> 00:53:42,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's ban her from coming into our house.</font>

991
00:53:43,129 --> 00:53:45,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Can all of you stay quiet?</font>

992
00:53:45,259 --> 00:53:47,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I will take care of it.</font>

993
00:53:47,029 --> 00:53:49,259
<font color=#FFFF00>How will you take care of this?</font>

994
00:53:50,189 --> 00:53:53,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey. Why are you acting like this?</font>

995
00:53:53,359 --> 00:53:56,329
<font color=#FFFF00>On whose side are you?</font>

996
00:53:56,729 --> 00:54:01,089
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. What does he plan to do?</font>

997
00:54:01,529 --> 00:54:02,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, dear.</font>

998
00:54:03,359 --> 00:54:05,129
<font color=#FFFF00>How does Seong Joon fit into this?</font>

999
00:54:05,729 --> 00:54:06,889
<font color=#FFFF00>What about him?</font>

1000
00:54:07,929 --> 00:54:09,859
<font color=#FFFF00>I mean...</font>

1001
00:54:09,859 --> 00:54:12,089
<font color=#FFFF00>it seemed like he's visiting Mr. Lee quite often recently.</font>

1002
00:54:12,189 --> 00:54:14,559
<font color=#FFFF00>I was wondering if Seong Joon was affected by this in any way.</font>

1003
00:54:15,529 --> 00:54:17,689
<font color=#FFFF00>- What? - Even Seong Joon?</font>

1004
00:54:20,529 --> 00:54:22,059
<font color=#FFFF00>(Inbox)</font>

1005
00:54:24,959 --> 00:54:26,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Director.</font>

1006
00:54:26,359 --> 00:54:28,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you waiting for my emails?</font>

1007
00:54:29,289 --> 00:54:31,489
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry I didn't send you an email.</font>

1008
00:54:32,489 --> 00:54:34,589
<font color=#FFFF00>I have a problem now.</font>

1009
00:54:34,959 --> 00:54:37,389
<font color=#FFFF00>I think it is about my grandmother,</font>

1010
00:54:37,789 --> 00:54:39,229
<font color=#FFFF00>but I know nothing about it.</font>

1011
00:54:39,229 --> 00:54:40,929
<font color=#FFFF00>And I can't ask her anything.</font>

1012
00:54:42,289 --> 00:54:44,789
<font color=#FFFF00>You said you were coming this weekend. I will wait for you.</font>

1013
00:54:45,289 --> 00:54:47,159
<font color=#FFFF00>I will tell you everything then.</font>

1014
00:54:47,729 --> 00:54:49,629
<font color=#FFFF00>I have three days left until the weekend.</font>

1015
00:54:50,089 --> 00:54:51,129
<font color=#FFFF00>I miss you.</font>

1016
00:55:00,459 --> 00:55:01,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you Oh Dong Hui?</font>

1017
00:55:02,929 --> 00:55:03,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Who are you?</font>

1018
00:55:04,859 --> 00:55:05,859
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

1019
00:55:09,789 --> 00:55:10,929
<font color=#FFFF00>- We got it. - Let's go.</font>

1020
00:55:10,989 --> 00:55:12,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this to me? What are you doing?</font>

1021
00:55:13,429 --> 00:55:16,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Let go of me.</font>

1022
00:55:48,389 --> 00:55:50,389
<font color=#FFFF00>- You are here. - Yes, sir.</font>

1023
00:55:53,429 --> 00:55:55,159
<font color=#FFFF00>You look good today.</font>

1024
00:55:55,929 --> 00:55:57,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Today is an important day for you.</font>

1025
00:55:58,429 --> 00:56:00,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Above all things,</font>

1026
00:56:00,289 --> 00:56:02,729
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to cause any harm to you and your brother.</font>

1027
00:56:03,859 --> 00:56:05,589
<font color=#FFFF00>So I dressed up.</font>

1028
00:56:08,929 --> 00:56:10,489
<font color=#FFFF00>That's very thoughtful of you.</font>

1029
00:56:12,129 --> 00:56:13,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Where's Sang Woo?</font>

1030
00:56:14,789 --> 00:56:17,159
<font color=#FFFF00>I will meet him in front of my house at seven o'clock.</font>

1031
00:56:17,459 --> 00:56:18,589
<font color=#FFFF00>That's good to know.</font>

1032
00:56:19,059 --> 00:56:21,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope it will be...</font>

1033
00:56:21,059 --> 00:56:23,289
<font color=#FFFF00>a meaningful day for you two.</font>

1034
00:56:24,189 --> 00:56:25,229
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope so too.</font>

1035
00:56:26,589 --> 00:56:29,689
<font color=#FFFF00>People must be curious...</font>

1036
00:56:29,789 --> 00:56:31,129
<font color=#FFFF00>about David Lee's brother.</font>

1037
00:56:31,889 --> 00:56:32,889
<font color=#FFFF00>You bet.</font>

1038
00:56:33,129 --> 00:56:35,389
<font color=#FFFF00>You won't be afraid of anything...</font>

1039
00:56:35,689 --> 00:56:37,159
<font color=#FFFF00>even in New York...</font>

1040
00:56:37,559 --> 00:56:39,489
<font color=#FFFF00>as long as you have Sang Woo with you.</font>

1041
00:56:40,259 --> 00:56:43,229
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why you need a brother.</font>

1042
00:56:45,189 --> 00:56:48,389
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess that's why my father left him to me.</font>

1043
00:56:49,059 --> 00:56:50,329
<font color=#FFFF00>So that I won't be lonely...</font>

1044
00:56:51,129 --> 00:56:53,629
<font color=#FFFF00>and live alone in this rough world.</font>

1045
00:56:55,929 --> 00:56:58,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Congratulations on the party.</font>

1046
00:57:00,189 --> 00:57:01,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you.</font>

1047
00:57:02,729 --> 00:57:04,889
<font color=#FFFF00>How did you know that?</font>

1048
00:57:06,829 --> 00:57:08,029
<font color=#FFFF00>When did you find it out?</font>

1049
00:57:09,189 --> 00:57:11,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I found out even before Seong Joon.</font>

1050
00:57:11,459 --> 00:57:13,389
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard it when I went to see Mal Ja.</font>

1051
00:57:14,859 --> 00:57:17,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that why you told me to go see Mal Ja?</font>

1052
00:57:20,959 --> 00:57:22,429
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

1053
00:57:25,089 --> 00:57:27,159
<font color=#FFFF00>You must've been through a lot of heartaches.</font>

1054
00:57:27,729 --> 00:57:29,059
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

1055
00:57:29,829 --> 00:57:32,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon said he'd take care of it.</font>

1056
00:57:32,359 --> 00:57:33,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Please give him a chance.</font>

1057
00:57:35,959 --> 00:57:38,789
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm so sorry for him. He must be miserable.</font>

1058
00:57:40,429 --> 00:57:41,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Uncle.</font>

1059
00:57:43,289 --> 00:57:45,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Does your family have hard feelings toward Hyun Woo?</font>

1060
00:57:47,689 --> 00:57:49,359
<font color=#FFFF00>It's all my fault.</font>

1061
00:57:50,089 --> 00:57:51,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Uncle.</font>

1062
00:57:52,989 --> 00:57:55,489
<font color=#FFFF00>I know it wouldn't make any difference even if I tell you this.</font>

1063
00:57:55,659 --> 00:57:57,759
<font color=#FFFF00>But I have to tell you this.</font>

1064
00:58:00,359 --> 00:58:03,389
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't want to tell you this though.</font>

1065
00:58:04,129 --> 00:58:05,629
<font color=#FFFF00>I know you've lived...</font>

1066
00:58:05,759 --> 00:58:07,659
<font color=#FFFF00>with guilt all your life.</font>

1067
00:58:08,489 --> 00:58:11,529
<font color=#FFFF00>If I can't help you, I don't want to give you a hard time at least.</font>

1068
00:58:11,789 --> 00:58:14,459
<font color=#FFFF00>But now that your family found it out,</font>

1069
00:58:15,359 --> 00:58:17,389
<font color=#FFFF00>you should know the truth.</font>

1070
00:58:18,629 --> 00:58:20,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop beating around the bush and just tell me.</font>

1071
00:58:22,389 --> 00:58:24,589
<font color=#FFFF00>The van incident.</font>

1072
00:58:25,789 --> 00:58:26,789
<font color=#FFFF00>In fact,</font>

1073
00:58:26,959 --> 00:58:30,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Guem Ja was going to give some money and reach an agreement.</font>

1074
00:58:30,329 --> 00:58:32,859
<font color=#FFFF00>But you kept insisting...</font>

1075
00:58:32,859 --> 00:58:35,729
<font color=#FFFF00>he was a drunkard and tried to call the police.</font>

1076
00:58:36,029 --> 00:58:38,089
<font color=#FFFF00>She were afraid of getting caught,</font>

1077
00:58:39,129 --> 00:58:40,659
<font color=#FFFF00>so she brought...</font>

1078
00:58:40,689 --> 00:58:42,959
<font color=#FFFF00>a false charge against Hyun Woo's father with Mal Ja...</font>

1079
00:58:44,129 --> 00:58:45,929
<font color=#FFFF00>to save her face.</font>

1080
00:58:48,329 --> 00:58:49,459
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you saying?</font>

1081
00:58:51,189 --> 00:58:52,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo's father...</font>

1082
00:58:53,389 --> 00:58:55,359
<font color=#FFFF00>was not drunk.</font>

1083
00:58:56,689 --> 00:58:58,129
<font color=#FFFF00>He already quit drinking.</font>

1084
00:58:59,789 --> 00:59:01,989
<font color=#FFFF00>He didn't even touch a drop of alcohol that day.</font>

1085
00:59:03,559 --> 00:59:06,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Uncle. You got the wrong person.</font>

1086
00:59:08,789 --> 00:59:09,859
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

1087
00:59:11,829 --> 00:59:15,689
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what's taking her so long.</font>

1088
00:59:15,759 --> 00:59:17,289
<font color=#FFFF00>And what's wrong with you?</font>

1089
00:59:18,929 --> 00:59:22,289
<font color=#FFFF00>I will talk to Jeong Eun once she comes out of the room.</font>

1090
00:59:22,989 --> 00:59:25,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Uncle, what's wrong? Wake up.</font>

1091
00:59:26,929 --> 00:59:29,129
<font color=#FFFF00>- What's going on? - I don't know.</font>

1092
00:59:29,459 --> 00:59:31,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Aunt! Grandmother!</font>

1093
00:59:32,829 --> 00:59:35,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Aunt! Grandmother! Please come here.</font>

1094
00:59:35,759 --> 00:59:37,429
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

1095
00:59:37,929 --> 00:59:39,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad, what's wrong?</font>

1096
00:59:40,529 --> 00:59:41,789
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on? Honey!</font>

1097
00:59:41,789 --> 00:59:43,259
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with him?</font>

1098
00:59:43,329 --> 00:59:44,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon! Grandmother!</font>

1099
00:59:44,459 --> 00:59:46,059
<font color=#FFFF00>We should take him to the hospital.</font>

1100
00:59:46,059 --> 00:59:47,559
<font color=#FFFF00>- What's wrong with him? - Dad.</font>

1101
00:59:47,629 --> 00:59:50,189
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dad, wake up. - Hurry.</font>

1102
00:59:50,229 --> 00:59:52,189
<font color=#FFFF00>- Gosh. - Hurry.</font>

1103
00:59:52,229 --> 00:59:53,789
<font color=#FFFF00>- What's wrong with him? - What should we do?</font>

1104
00:59:55,259 --> 00:59:57,489
<font color=#FFFF00>What should I do?</font>

1105
01:00:09,329 --> 01:00:12,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Sang Woo must be running a little late, sir.</font>

1106
01:00:14,059 --> 01:00:15,059
<font color=#FFFF00>He'll come soon.</font>

1107
01:00:20,029 --> 01:00:21,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon, where's your car?</font>

1108
01:00:22,729 --> 01:00:23,989
<font color=#FFFF00>It's down the street.</font>

1109
01:00:24,529 --> 01:00:26,389
<font color=#FFFF00>That's too far.</font>

1110
01:00:32,529 --> 01:00:33,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

1111
01:00:35,729 --> 01:00:37,189
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing now?</font>

1112
01:00:40,259 --> 01:00:41,559
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you forget our plan?</font>

1113
01:00:43,559 --> 01:00:46,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo, Dad is sick.</font>

1114
01:00:56,229 --> 01:00:58,829
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo, I'm sorry. I will talk to you later.</font>

1115
01:01:31,759 --> 01:01:32,759
<font color=#FFFF00>It's me.</font>

1116
01:01:33,559 --> 01:01:35,329
<font color=#FFFF00>How's Han Seong Hoon's...</font>

1117
01:01:35,889 --> 01:01:37,189
<font color=#FFFF00>theme park business going?</font>

1118
01:01:59,359 --> 01:02:00,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Honey.</font>

1119
01:02:00,759 --> 01:02:02,289
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong, Seong Hoon?</font>

1120
01:02:02,959 --> 01:02:05,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon, we have a problem.</font>

1121
01:02:05,789 --> 01:02:06,889
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

1122
01:02:07,129 --> 01:02:09,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Where should I go? Which way?</font>

1123
01:02:10,059 --> 01:02:12,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon. Seong Hoon! What's wrong?</font>

1124
01:02:13,159 --> 01:02:15,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

1125
01:02:16,059 --> 01:02:18,559
<font color=#FFFF00>What should I do? We are in trouble.</font>

1126
01:02:18,959 --> 01:02:19,959
<font color=#FFFF00>My business...</font>

1127
01:02:20,789 --> 01:02:23,089
<font color=#FFFF00>- was a fraud. - What?</font>

1128
01:02:27,029 --> 01:02:29,529
<font color=#FFFF00>I should go.</font>

1129
01:02:29,859 --> 01:02:31,359
<font color=#FFFF00>I should go catch them.</font>

1130
01:03:01,859 --> 01:03:03,829
<font color=#FFFF00>(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

1131
01:03:05,029 --> 01:03:07,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Please save my children.</font>

1132
01:03:07,889 --> 01:03:10,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think they'll think of you as family knowing you're my brother?</font>

1133
01:03:11,829 --> 01:03:13,129
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want...</font>

1134
01:03:13,389 --> 01:03:16,059
<font color=#FFFF00>our family to know that...</font>

1135
01:03:16,459 --> 01:03:18,289
<font color=#FFFF00>you are Mr. Lee's brother.</font>

1136
01:03:18,789 --> 01:03:20,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui, are you in there?</font>

1137
01:03:21,129 --> 01:03:23,959
<font color=#FFFF00>- They've moved out. - What?</font>

1138
01:03:24,259 --> 01:03:27,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Let go of me! Why are you doing this to me?</font>

